about.summary: Provides a collection of features, decompositions, statistical summaries and graphics functions for the analysing tidy time series data. The package name 'feasts' is an acronym comprising of its key features:  Feature Extraction And Statistics for Time Series.

name: r-feasts
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.1.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-feasts
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/feasts_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/feasts/feasts_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 36146eaadbe739ede3a59436a70c9e1c3c4a9ff990dfafca17b6b9f67116f44b

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-dplyr >=0.8.0
    - r-fabletools
    - r-ggplot2 >=3.0.0
    - r-rlang >=0.2.0
    - r-scales
    - r-tibble >=1.4.1
    - r-tidyr >=0.8.3
    - r-tsibble >=0.8.0
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-dplyr >=0.8.0
    - r-fabletools
    - r-ggplot2 >=3.0.0
    - r-rlang >=0.2.0
    - r-scales
    - r-tibble >=1.4.1
    - r-tidyr >=0.8.3
    - r-tsibble >=0.8.0

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('feasts')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('feasts')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://feasts.tidyverts.org/
  license: GPL-3
  summary: 'Provides a collection of features, decompositions, statistical summaries and graphics
    functions for the analysing tidy time series data. The package name ''feasts'' is
    an acronym comprising of its key features:  Feature Extraction And Statistics for
    Time Series.'
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - philip-khor
